      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>遵大路兮，摻執子之袪兮。無我惡兮，不寁故也。
遵大路兮，摻執子之手兮。無我魗兮，不寁好也。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>1 Along the highway.
I hold you by the cuff.
Do not hate me ; —
Old intercourse should not be suddenly broken off.

2 Along the high way, •
I hold you by the hand.
Do not think me vile ; —
Old friendship should not hastily be broken off.</seg>
      </tuv>
